1
00:01:28,132 --> 00:01:32,807
[Adapted from Che Ye Liu Xiang's
novel of the same name]

2
00:01:34,650 --> 00:01:38,858
Xiao Fan, I'm going to stay here
with Lv Qing for a while.

3
00:01:38,858 --> 00:01:42,973
So... I'm afraid you'll have to move out.

4
00:01:51,566 --> 00:01:53,400
Let's get to know each other. I'm Li Wen Xi.

5
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,900
Who is Li Wen Xi?

6
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:57,983
He's Lv Qing's childhood sweetheart.

7
00:01:57,983 --> 00:02:00,816
Do you know what your most valuable trait is?

8
00:02:00,816 --> 00:02:03,037
It's that you're sensible.

9
00:02:04,650 --> 00:02:05,971
Oh.

10
00:02:30,358 --> 00:02:31,775
Big Bro.

11
00:02:31,775 --> 00:02:35,912
The soup in the pot
will be ready in half an hour.

12
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:08,465
I...

13
00:03:13,233 --> 00:03:15,023
I'll be leaving now.

14
00:03:58,733 --> 00:04:01,233
It's the middle of the night,
and you're crouching by the door.

15
00:04:01,233 --> 00:04:03,775
- Auntie Lin.
- Aren't you at school?

16
00:04:03,775 --> 00:04:05,525
Auntie Lin.

17
00:04:05,525 --> 00:04:07,816
The dormitory closed early.

18
00:04:07,816 --> 00:04:09,275
I didn't make it back in time.

19
00:04:09,275 --> 00:04:12,472
Why were you out so late?

20
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:16,358
Xiao Fan.

21
00:04:16,358 --> 00:04:18,733
Let me tell you.

22
00:04:18,733 --> 00:04:22,952
You and Lv Qing are at the same school.

23
00:04:23,983 --> 00:04:26,441
Even though Lv Qing has graduated,

24
00:04:26,441 --> 00:04:29,275
there are still many alumni at the school.

25
00:04:29,275 --> 00:04:30,608
You must behave well at school.

26
00:04:30,608 --> 00:04:33,441
Don't embarrass Lv Qing.

27
00:04:33,441 --> 00:04:34,928
I understand.

28
00:04:37,608 --> 00:04:39,065
I understand.

29
00:04:42,191 --> 00:04:44,075
Yeah.

30
00:04:45,566 --> 00:04:47,658
I've embarrassed him.

31
00:06:04,775 --> 00:06:06,066
Xiao Fan.

32
00:06:06,066 --> 00:06:07,483
Come sit here.

33
00:06:12,108 --> 00:06:13,400
Xiao Fan.

34
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:15,483
You're graduating soon, right?

35
00:06:15,483 --> 00:06:17,383
Yes, Mr. Bei.

36
00:06:18,233 --> 00:06:20,496
Do you want to get a bachelor's degree?

37
00:06:24,983 --> 00:06:26,546
I don't want to study anymore.

38
00:06:29,233 --> 00:06:31,441
If you don't want to, then don't.

39
00:06:31,441 --> 00:06:33,900
Starting work early isn't a bad thing.

40
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:35,358
I'll be going now.

41
00:06:35,358 --> 00:06:36,983
Wait a moment.

42
00:06:36,983 --> 00:06:39,087
Regarding Xiao Fan's job...

43
00:06:42,649 --> 00:06:46,733
I think we should respect his decision.

44
00:06:46,733 --> 00:06:50,005
He is a man of his own mind.

45
00:06:51,858 --> 00:06:53,950
Bye-bye.

46
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,083
<i>Xiao Fan.</i>

47
00:07:14,083 --> 00:07:16,333
<i>Here's the number for your new workplace.</i>

48
00:07:16,333 --> 00:07:19,083
<i>Since you chose to start working early,</i>

49
00:07:19,083 --> 00:07:20,398
<i>do work hard.</i>

50
00:07:20,398 --> 00:07:22,916
<i>The Bei family will treat you well.</i>

51
00:07:34,608 --> 00:07:35,775
Hello.

52
00:07:35,775 --> 00:07:36,983
I'm Lu Xiao Fan.

53
00:07:36,983 --> 00:07:39,066
I'm here to report for duty today.

54
00:07:39,066 --> 00:07:40,066
Xiao Fan, you're here.

55
00:07:40,066 --> 00:07:41,525
Come, have a seat. Come on.

56
00:07:41,525 --> 00:07:42,775
Come over here.

57
00:07:42,775 --> 00:07:44,191
I've been waiting for you.

58
00:07:44,191 --> 00:07:45,275
Come, sit.

59
00:07:45,275 --> 00:07:46,400
Okay.

60
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:48,691
Xiao Fan, work hard.

61
00:07:48,691 --> 00:07:50,475
I have high hopes for you.

62
00:08:28,916 --> 00:08:32,166
<i>Bro, you haven't been back in so long.</i>

63
00:08:32,166 --> 00:08:34,250
<i>You didn't even come visit me.</i>

64
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:37,791
<i>That annoying Lu Xiao Fan
watches DVDs in the living room every day.</i>

65
00:08:37,791 --> 00:08:39,875
<i>He whimpers late at night.
It's so annoying.</i>

66
00:08:39,875 --> 00:08:42,166
<i>You should find something to do too.</i>

67
00:08:42,166 --> 00:08:44,625
<i>I'll go back once every few weeks.</i>

68
00:08:44,625 --> 00:08:47,000
<i>I'm busy. That's all.</i>

69
00:09:05,264 --> 00:09:09,851
[Two years later]

70
00:09:23,716 --> 00:09:25,217
[Xiao Ping Calling]

71
00:09:28,143 --> 00:09:29,973
<i>Xiao Fan. What's the emergency?</i>

72
00:09:29,973 --> 00:09:31,435
<i>Can't you call after work?</i>

73
00:09:31,435 --> 00:09:34,203
Big Bro, didn't you page me?

74
00:09:34,976 --> 00:09:36,838
<i>Mom booked a train for next week.</i>

75
00:09:36,838 --> 00:09:38,203
<i>Remember to go pick her up.</i>

76
00:09:38,203 --> 00:09:40,286
Mom is coming to Yunjing?

77
00:09:40,833 --> 00:09:41,958
<i>Have Old Wu pick her up.</i>

78
00:09:41,958 --> 00:09:43,975
<i>I think he's a steadier driver.</i>

79
00:09:43,975 --> 00:09:46,813
<i>You haven't thought of coming home in ages.</i>

80
00:09:46,813 --> 00:09:48,542
<i>By the way, Mom specifically said</i>

81
00:09:48,542 --> 00:09:50,842
<i>she wants to see Lv Xin.</i>

82
00:09:52,542 --> 00:09:53,836
Mom wants to see Lv Xin too?

83
00:09:53,836 --> 00:09:55,167
<i>What's wrong?</i>

84
00:09:55,167 --> 00:09:57,867
<i>Can't a mother-in-law see her daughter-in-law?</i>

85
00:09:57,867 --> 00:09:59,375
<i>Return tickets are hard to come by.</i>

86
00:09:59,375 --> 00:10:00,708
<i>Book one as soon as possible.</i>

87
00:10:00,708 --> 00:10:02,060
She's taking a plane?

88
00:10:02,060 --> 00:10:03,917
<i>It's not easy for Mom to visit Yunjing.</i>

89
00:10:03,917 --> 00:10:06,420
<i>We should let her enjoy herself.</i>

90
00:10:06,420 --> 00:10:08,980
<i>Fine. I'll pay for the ticket.</i>

91
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:11,696
But you'll need a letter of recommendation.

92
00:10:11,696 --> 00:10:14,083
<i>Just have Old Wu book it.</i>

93
00:10:14,083 --> 00:10:16,292
<i>Does the Bei family need
a letter of recommendation to book tickets?</i>

94
00:10:17,333 --> 00:10:18,652
<i>Oh, right.</i>

95
00:10:18,652 --> 00:10:20,667
<i>Mom said she's bringing the little one along.</i>

96
00:10:20,667 --> 00:10:22,167
<i>To let her see the world.</i>

97
00:10:22,167 --> 00:10:23,667
Okay, I understand.

98
00:10:23,667 --> 00:10:25,501
<i>All right. I'll hang up now.</i>

99
00:10:26,250 --> 00:10:27,871
<i>Be sensible.</i>

100
00:10:40,730 --> 00:10:42,146
Auntie Lin.

101
00:10:42,146 --> 00:10:43,230
Is Mr. Bei not home?

102
00:10:43,230 --> 00:10:44,271
Mr. Bei?

103
00:10:44,271 --> 00:10:45,480
He's at a meeting out of town.

104
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,581
He won't be back for half a month.

105
00:10:57,625 --> 00:11:00,346
Is something wrong with your family again?

106
00:11:01,563 --> 00:11:04,313
My parents are coming to Yunjing.

107
00:11:04,313 --> 00:11:05,855
Then just host them normally.

108
00:11:05,855 --> 00:11:08,696
Don't trouble Mr. Bei with everything.

109
00:11:10,396 --> 00:11:11,688
Lv Xin.

110
00:11:11,688 --> 00:11:14,048
- Lv Xin.
- What?

111
00:11:15,355 --> 00:11:16,646
Nothing.

112
00:11:16,646 --> 00:11:18,143
It's nothing.

113
00:11:19,355 --> 00:11:21,569
Help me take this inside.

114
00:12:03,355 --> 00:12:04,430
You're here!

115
00:12:05,313 --> 00:12:06,480
Sir.

116
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,855
Any new releases lately?

117
00:12:07,855 --> 00:12:10,574
Sure. Plenty. Which one do you want?

118
00:12:12,813 --> 00:12:13,813
What's that one?

119
00:12:13,813 --> 00:12:15,105
A martial arts film.

120
00:12:15,105 --> 00:12:16,980
Brigitte Lin is cross-dressing.

121
00:12:16,980 --> 00:12:18,467
I'll take that one.

122
00:12:19,438 --> 00:12:21,521
I like Brigitte Lin, too.

123
00:12:21,521 --> 00:12:23,105
Besides Brigitte Lin,

124
00:12:23,105 --> 00:12:25,105
no one can play Lian Ni Shang well.

125
00:12:25,105 --> 00:12:26,771
It's a pity Lian Ni Shang
had a humble background.

126
00:12:26,771 --> 00:12:29,771
If she hadn't fallen for
Zhuo Yi Hang from a noble family,

127
00:12:29,771 --> 00:12:32,563
she wouldn't have ended up like this.

128
00:12:32,563 --> 00:12:34,101
What a pity.

129
00:12:39,896 --> 00:12:42,063
- I'm off, sir.
- Okay.

130
00:12:42,063 --> 00:12:44,044
Take care. Come again.

131
00:12:54,146 --> 00:12:55,855
- Auntie Lin.
- Oh.

132
00:12:55,855 --> 00:12:57,230
Xiao Fan.

133
00:12:57,230 --> 00:12:59,855
You're back so late.
I didn't save any dinner for you.

134
00:12:59,855 --> 00:13:01,271
It's okay, Auntie Lin.

135
00:13:01,271 --> 00:13:03,480
Go and get some rest.

136
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,543
I'll leave you to it then.

137
00:14:00,403 --> 00:14:03,396
- Hello?
<i>- It's so convenient with a workplace phone.</i>

138
00:14:03,396 --> 00:14:05,980
Have you arranged for Mom's meal with Lv Xin?

139
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:06,980
<i>I'm working on it.</i>

140
00:14:06,980 --> 00:14:09,480
<i>Is it so much trouble for Mom
to see her daughter-in-law?</i>

141
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,896
<i>Geez.</i>

142
00:14:10,896 --> 00:14:12,271
Don't worry.

143
00:14:12,271 --> 00:14:13,854
I'm at work. I'll get it sorted.

144
00:14:13,854 --> 00:14:14,896
<i>Who are you trying to kid?</i>

145
00:14:14,896 --> 00:14:18,079
<i>With that job of yours,
what could be so urgent?</i>

146
00:14:47,234 --> 00:14:48,586
<i>Who is it?</i>

147
00:14:50,230 --> 00:14:52,238
It's me.

148
00:14:54,313 --> 00:14:55,521
Big Bro.

149
00:14:55,521 --> 00:14:57,688
Long time no see.

150
00:14:57,688 --> 00:15:00,103
What is it this time?

151
00:15:01,230 --> 00:15:03,771
Does your family need money again?

152
00:15:03,771 --> 00:15:07,188
Or is your brother unhappy with his job again?

153
00:15:07,188 --> 00:15:09,730
Or something else?

154
00:15:09,730 --> 00:15:13,605
My mom said she wants to visit me in Yunjing.

155
00:15:13,605 --> 00:15:17,021
Can't you just host them yourself?

156
00:15:17,021 --> 00:15:20,950
She also wants to see Lv Xin.

157
00:15:23,146 --> 00:15:27,271
Maybe you could give her a call?

158
00:15:27,271 --> 00:15:29,571
Fine. I got it.

159
00:15:31,813 --> 00:15:33,480
Big Bro.

160
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,476
Are you really not going to eat?

161
00:15:36,230 --> 00:15:37,669
I'm not hungry.

162
00:15:39,313 --> 00:15:41,067
Then...

163
00:15:42,396 --> 00:15:44,127
I'll get going.

164
00:16:07,646 --> 00:16:10,230
I'm going to stay with Lv Qing for a while.
[Two years ago]

165
00:16:10,230 --> 00:16:13,094
I'm afraid you'll have to move out.

166
00:16:20,146 --> 00:16:22,063
Big Bro.

167
00:16:22,063 --> 00:16:24,662
I'll get going.

168
00:16:39,646 --> 00:16:40,771
See?

169
00:16:40,771 --> 00:16:44,230
He's even afraid to face me.

170
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:47,188
How can he have the courage or capital

171
00:16:47,188 --> 00:16:49,184
to face your mother?

172
00:16:52,688 --> 00:16:55,188
You know better than anyone

173
00:16:55,188 --> 00:16:57,685
how your mother treated me back then.

174
00:16:59,271 --> 00:17:02,313
You want to know his reaction too, right?

175
00:17:02,313 --> 00:17:04,771
Will he cry?

176
00:17:04,771 --> 00:17:08,238
Will he... fight for it?

177
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:12,646
You're too proud to ask him yourself.

178
00:17:12,646 --> 00:17:18,107
Is he... simply looking for your help?

179
00:17:24,605 --> 00:17:26,896
It's for the best.

180
00:17:26,896 --> 00:17:30,271
Rather than waiting for your mother
to find out and take action.

181
00:17:30,271 --> 00:17:32,153
It's better to break up sooner.

182
00:17:48,938 --> 00:17:51,313
I'm really curious.

183
00:17:51,313 --> 00:17:54,405
Why did you fall for someone like him?

184
00:17:57,938 --> 00:18:00,802
Aren't you being a bit too nosy?

185
00:18:01,771 --> 00:18:07,311
Our only connection now
is that money in Gangcheng.

186
00:18:10,730 --> 00:18:15,060
I can help you with your goal now.

187
00:18:17,355 --> 00:18:20,017
I'm the one helping you.

188
00:18:22,063 --> 00:18:24,521
Give the information from the old man

189
00:18:24,521 --> 00:18:27,563
directly to Li Wen Xi.

190
00:18:27,563 --> 00:18:30,321
Let him handle the overseas operations.

191
00:18:32,230 --> 00:18:34,438
It's a partnership.

192
00:18:34,438 --> 00:18:38,563
In Gangcheng, there aren't many companies

193
00:18:38,563 --> 00:18:40,571
that can buy out your mother's shares.

194
00:18:47,563 --> 00:18:50,696
I don't want to be controlled by my mother.

195
00:18:52,813 --> 00:18:54,896
<i>Wait a second.</i>

196
00:18:54,896 --> 00:18:57,446
<i>Regarding Xiao Fan's job...</i>

197
00:19:01,938 --> 00:19:05,771
<i>I think we should respect his wishes.</i>

198
00:19:05,771 --> 00:19:09,117
<i>He is a man of his own mind.</i>

199
00:19:11,563 --> 00:19:14,480
Is that section chief easy to get along with?

200
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:16,313
I need to give him a little nudge.

201
00:19:16,313 --> 00:19:18,355
He's timid.

202
00:19:18,355 --> 00:19:21,271
Deliver the two cartons
of cigarettes in the trunk for me.

203
00:19:21,271 --> 00:19:22,938
We can't let the relationship sour.

204
00:19:22,938 --> 00:19:26,146
This is our new
deputy section chief, Lu Xiao Fan.

205
00:19:26,146 --> 00:19:29,605
From now on, please support him in his work.

206
00:19:29,605 --> 00:19:33,032
If he adjusts well, let him stay there for now.

207
00:19:34,188 --> 00:19:36,023
As for other matters...

208
00:19:37,188 --> 00:19:38,855
Two years.

209
00:19:38,855 --> 00:19:42,271
Two years is enough to get
my mother's shares out of there.

210
00:19:42,271 --> 00:19:44,134
We'll talk about matters again then.

211
00:19:53,855 --> 00:19:54,980
Bottoms up!

212
00:19:54,980 --> 00:19:56,480
Bottoms up!

213
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:57,813
Bottoms up!

214
00:19:57,813 --> 00:19:59,480
Bottoms up!

215
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:02,021
It's your birthday,
but all the drinks are coming my way.

216
00:20:03,980 --> 00:20:06,088
Isn't that Lu Xiao Fan?

217
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:17,090
He fled quite quickly.

218
00:20:23,188 --> 00:20:25,646
<i>Thank you for taking care of me, Big Bro.</i>

219
00:20:25,646 --> 00:20:27,531
<i>I'm very grateful to you.</i>

220
00:20:30,188 --> 00:20:31,605
Did you tell him?

221
00:20:31,605 --> 00:20:33,188
I just wanted you to experience

222
00:20:33,188 --> 00:20:35,230
what it's like to have one on each arm.

223
00:20:35,230 --> 00:20:37,094
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

224
00:21:56,583 --> 00:22:00,716
[Two years later]
[Year 1992]

225
00:22:06,063 --> 00:22:07,771
Isn't this Xiao Fan?

226
00:22:07,771 --> 00:22:09,896
Want to join us for some high-end abalone?

227
00:22:09,896 --> 00:22:11,551
Your brother is here, too.

228
00:22:19,313 --> 00:22:24,608
Zi Yang, I'm busy, so I won't be going.

229
00:22:28,313 --> 00:22:30,137
All for nothing.

230
00:22:34,896 --> 00:22:35,938
My dear Young Master Bei,

231
00:22:35,938 --> 00:22:39,129
how did you get tangled up with him again?

232
00:22:40,271 --> 00:22:41,521
I didn't.

233
00:22:41,521 --> 00:22:42,813
Look at you.

234
00:22:42,813 --> 00:22:44,313
You went to all that trouble

235
00:22:44,313 --> 00:22:46,480
to finally stop
being controlled by your mother.

236
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:48,646
And it turns out it was all for Lu Xiao Fan.

237
00:22:48,646 --> 00:22:49,938
Fine.

238
00:22:49,938 --> 00:22:50,938
Stop being smart.

239
00:22:50,938 --> 00:22:52,730
What are you trying to say?

240
00:22:52,730 --> 00:22:55,730
You've helped him a lot,
both openly and secretly, these past two years.

241
00:22:55,730 --> 00:22:58,438
In your heart,
he's no longer just a pageboy, right?

242
00:22:58,438 --> 00:23:01,146
If you were worried about your mom
harming him back then,

243
00:23:01,146 --> 00:23:03,599
you could've just told him directly.

244
00:23:09,105 --> 00:23:10,980
I want to go buy a cake.

245
00:23:10,980 --> 00:23:13,063
Today is Xiao Fan's birthday.

246
00:23:13,063 --> 00:23:14,563
So, you do know how to coax him.

247
00:23:14,563 --> 00:23:16,146
They say a rabbit doesn't eat
the grass near its burrow,

248
00:23:16,146 --> 00:23:18,313
but you're even going back for old grass.

249
00:23:18,313 --> 00:23:21,415
I really don't see
what's so charming about Lu Xiao Fan.

250
00:23:22,313 --> 00:23:24,116
Of course you don't.

251
00:23:26,188 --> 00:23:29,730
When I was little,
we had a nanny named Mrs. Zhang.

252
00:23:29,730 --> 00:23:31,438
I was very attached to her.

253
00:23:31,438 --> 00:23:33,730
I would only eat her cooking.

254
00:23:33,730 --> 00:23:36,521
One day, when she came upstairs
to bring me food,

255
00:23:36,521 --> 00:23:38,813
the spoon fell on the floor.

256
00:23:38,813 --> 00:23:42,563
She picked it up and handed it back to me.

257
00:23:42,563 --> 00:23:47,355
I was thinking, if I were her own child,

258
00:23:47,355 --> 00:23:48,771
would she have gone to the trouble

259
00:23:48,771 --> 00:23:51,598
of going downstairs to get me a new spoon?

260
00:23:53,438 --> 00:23:57,612
Are you saying
Lu Xiao Fan would get you a new spoon?

261
00:23:59,563 --> 00:24:02,938
Now, my spoon won't fall on the floor.

262
00:24:02,938 --> 00:24:04,023
Fine, fine, fine.

263
00:24:04,023 --> 00:24:05,944
Here we go again.

264
00:24:07,605 --> 00:24:09,480
Don't tease him anymore.

265
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,639
Lu Xiao Fan takes things too seriously.

266
00:24:24,771 --> 00:24:26,189
<i>Come back.</i>

267
00:24:47,063 --> 00:24:48,771
Big Bro.

268
00:24:48,771 --> 00:24:50,975
Why are you back?

269
00:24:59,730 --> 00:25:02,943
They gave me an extra one,
so I brought it back.

270
00:25:08,396 --> 00:25:13,600
Big Bro, can you say "Happy Birthday" to me?

271
00:25:16,980 --> 00:25:18,980
Happy birthday.

272
00:25:45,271 --> 00:25:46,966
Wait a second.

273
00:26:02,146 --> 00:26:03,617
There.

274
00:26:08,313 --> 00:26:11,938
Happy birthday to you.

275
00:26:11,938 --> 00:26:15,813
Happy birthday to you.

276
00:26:15,813 --> 00:26:19,905
Happy birthday to you.

277
00:26:22,188 --> 00:26:26,238
Happy birthday to you.

278
00:26:33,021 --> 00:26:35,188
All right.

279
00:26:35,188 --> 00:26:37,171
Blow out the candle.

280
00:26:56,146 --> 00:26:57,987
Happy birthday.

281
00:26:58,896 --> 00:27:00,558
Thank you, Big Bro.

282
00:27:07,438 --> 00:27:10,028
This cake is as delicious as always.

283
00:27:13,938 --> 00:27:15,480
The rest of the movie isn't that good.

284
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:19,011
Big Bro, why don't you watch
the international news?

285
00:27:20,396 --> 00:27:22,396
It's fine.

286
00:27:22,396 --> 00:27:24,480
I can watch the tape anytime.

287
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:26,813
It's okay.

288
00:27:26,813 --> 00:27:28,688
No, really. I'll stop it right now.

289
00:27:28,688 --> 00:27:31,083
I said, I want to watch it.

290
00:27:33,646 --> 00:27:35,149
Get back here.

291
00:29:56,855 --> 00:30:00,852
Tomorrow, make me some porridge.

292
00:30:23,479 --> 00:30:26,135
[Bei Lv Qing: Call when free]

293
00:30:46,230 --> 00:30:47,563
<i>Why did you take so long to call back?</i>

294
00:30:47,563 --> 00:30:49,230
I was at the office.

295
00:30:49,230 --> 00:30:50,730
It wasn't convenient.

296
00:30:50,730 --> 00:30:51,813
<i>I'm at the supermarket.</i>

297
00:30:51,813 --> 00:30:54,021
<i>What do you need? I'll get it all at once.</i>

298
00:30:54,021 --> 00:30:56,563
I bought scallions, ginger,
and garlic last time.

299
00:30:56,563 --> 00:30:59,146
And then... get half a chicken.

300
00:30:59,146 --> 00:31:01,563
And a fish, anything that's fresh.

301
00:31:01,563 --> 00:31:02,730
Get some leafy greens, too.

302
00:31:02,730 --> 00:31:04,021
Buy whatever you want to eat.

303
00:31:04,021 --> 00:31:05,896
Oh, right. Get some eggs, too.

304
00:31:05,896 --> 00:31:07,604
<i>Okay, I got it.</i>

305
00:31:07,604 --> 00:31:09,521
Just buy whatever you like.

306
00:31:09,521 --> 00:31:10,855
<i>Go to my place and wait for me.</i>

307
00:31:10,855 --> 00:31:12,811
<i>I'll be back soon.</i>

